quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,S tme$ôust akked tzemmurt
  95,2,S udrar n Sina
  95,3,Akked temdint agi n laman
  95,4,Ni$ Nxelq ed amdan d ûûam
  95,5,"Sinna, Nerra t d aneggaru ineggura"
  95,6,"Kkes ed wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, i nitni arraz imezgi"
  95,7,"Ihi, d acu, deffir waya, ara k iskiddben f uqeîîi"
  95,8,Day Öebbi maççi d Imxeyyeô n yimêaddan